I17whichever is most cost-effective for the Government considering all operational, travel, and transportation requirements incident to such change of station; and

I12(ii) from the customary port of debarkation which has been designated by the Government as most cost-effective for the Government considering all operational, travel, and transportation requirements incident to such change of station to the new duty station.

