I12(1) is retired, or is placed on the temporary disability retired list, under chapter 61 of title 10; or

I12(2) is retired with pay under any other law, or, immediately following at least eight years of continuous active duty with no single break therein of more than 90 days, is discharged with separation pay or severance pay or is involuntarily released from active duty with separation pay or readjustment pay.

